snippet.title: Seven Minutes Full Playthrough (No Commentary, Both Endings)
snippet.description:
Programming, Graphics, and Design by Tuukka Virtanen
Music by Erkka Virtanen
Inspired by cactus (Jonatan Söderström)

Released February 23, 2008 for Windows
Made with Game Maker in one week for Cactus' Winter Competition

Play the Game: https://web.archive.org/web/20100108001507/http://gamemakergames.com/?a=view&id=6520
More Information: https://www.mobygames.com/game/33213/seven-minutes/

0:00 1st Playthrough
5:50 Leave Ending
6:55 2nd Playthrough
14:23 Stay Ending
